#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:81
msgid "Sea Pickle"
msgstr "ヒカリボヤ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:82
msgid ""
"Sea pickles grow on dead brain coral blocks and provide light when "
"underwater. They come in 4 sizes that vary in brightness."
msgstr ""
"死した脳サンゴブロックに生え、水中での光源となるヒカリボヤ。明るさの異なる4種"
"類のサイズがあります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:83
msgid ""
"It can only be placed on top of dead brain coral blocks. Placing a sea "
"pickle on another sea pickle will make it grow and brighter."
msgstr ""
"死した脳サンゴブロックの上にしか置けません。ヒカリボヤを別のヒカリボヤの上に"
"置くと成長し、明るくなります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:84
msgid "Glows in the water"
msgstr "水中で成長"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:84
msgid "4 possible sizes"
msgstr "4種類のサイズが可能"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:84
msgid "Grows on dead brain coral block"
msgstr "死した脳サンゴブロックに生育"

